Repeat program 3-> make app

Open docker

Exit

Docker build -t <username>/app1-k8s:latest .

Docker push <username>/app1-k8s:latest

Make deployment.yml and service.yml

Kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
Kubectl apply -f service.yaml

Kubectl get pods 
Kubectl get svc

Kubectl scale deployment/hw-deployment--replicas=3

Change deployment.yaml
Spec containers -> image -> username/app1: latest 

Kubectl get deployment 
Kubectl get pods
Kubectl port-forward svc/hw-service 5000:5000

Then go to localhost:5000
